---
layout: layouts/base
---
<header id="about" class="section">
    <div class="t-container">
        {% include 'components/avatar.njk' %}
        <h1>
            <span class="t-visually-hidden">{{ site.author }}</span>
            {% include 'assets/logo.svg' %}
        </h1>
        <p><span class="emoji" aria-hidden="true">ðŸ‘‹</span> Hi, Iâ€™m {{ site.author }}, a multidisciplinary designer with {% experience %}+ years of experience. Originally from Lviv, Ukraine, I currently reside in {{ site.location }}. I care about form and function and believe in the power of simplicity.</p>
        <p>I currently spend my days designing at <a href="https://mywallst.com" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank">MyWallSt</a>. Previously, I have had the privilege to improve products used and loved by many users, and these are some of the clients:</p>
        {% if clients %}
            <ol class="clients t-list-horizontal">
                {% for client in clients %}
                    <li class="t-list-horizontal--item t-list-horizontal--item--distance-2">
                        {% if client.url %}
                            <a href="{{ client.url | url }}" rel="noopener noreferrer nofollow" target="_blank" title="{{ client.title }}">
                                {% include 'clients/' + client.title | slug + '.svg' %}
                            </a>
                        {% else %}
                            {% include 'clients/' + client.title | slug + '.svg' %}
                        {% endif %}
                    </li>
                {% endfor %}
            </ol>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
</header>

<section id="works" class="section">
    <div class="t-container">
        <h2>Case studies</h2>
        <p>My portfolio includes 50+ projects, hereâ€™s the selected one:</p>
    </div>
    <ol>
        {% for work in collections.work %}
            {% if work.url != false %}
                <li class="work work--reels">
                    <a class="work-link t-hover--2" href="{{ work.url | url }}" rel="bookmark" target="_parent">
                        {% thumbnail work.data.thumbnail, work.data.title %}
                        <div class="content">
                            <h3>{% if work.data.client %}{{ work.data.client }}: {% endif %}{{ work.data.title }}</h3>
                            {% if work.data.description %}
                                <p>{{ work.data.description }}</p>
                            {% endif %}
                        </div>
                    </a>
                </li>
            {% endif %}
        {% endfor %}
    </ol>
</section>
